39/*
40 * Print name of symbol. Return number of characters printed.
41 */
42int
43print_name_only (Sym *self)
44{
45 const char *name = self->name;
46 const char *filename;
47 char *demangled = 0;
48 char buf[PATH_MAX];
49 int size = 0;
50
51 if (name)
52 {
53 if (!bsd_style_output && demangle)
54 {
55 demangled = bfd_demangle (core_bfd, name, DMGL_ANSI | DMGL_PARAMS);
56 if (demangled)
57 name = demangled;
58 }
59 printf ("%s", name);
60 size = strlen (name);
61 if ((line_granularity || inline_file_names) && self->file)
62 {
63 filename = self->file->name;
64 if (!print_path)
65 {
66 filename = strrchr (filename, '/');
67 if (filename)
68 {
69 ++filename;
70 }
71 else
72 {
73 filename = self->file->name;
74 }
75 }
76 if (line_granularity)
77 {
78 sprintf (buf, " (%s:%d @ %lx)", filename, self->line_num,
79 (unsigned long) self->addr);
80 }
81 else
82 {
83 sprintf (buf, " (%s:%d)", filename, self->line_num);
84 }
85 printf ("%s", buf);
86 size += strlen (buf);
87 }
88 if (demangled)
89 {
90 free (demangled);
91 }
92 DBG (DFNDEBUG, printf ("{%d} ", self->cg.top_order));
93 DBG (PROPDEBUG, printf ("%4.0f%% ", 100.0 * self->cg.prop.fract));
94 }
95 return size;
96}

99void
100print_name (Sym *self)
101{
102 print_name_only (self);
103
104 if (self->cg.cyc.num != 0)
105 {
106 printf (_(" <cycle %d>"), self->cg.cyc.num);
107 }
108 if (self->cg.index != 0)
109 {
110 if (self->cg.print_flag)
111 {
112 printf (" [%d]", self->cg.index);
113 }
114 else
115 {
116 printf (" (%d)", self->cg.index);
117 }
118 }
